 come together to collectively serve as a modern watchdog, more vigilant and forceful than one person could ever be.\"<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2017/05/31/new-york-times-buyouts/102344652/|title=The New York Times offers newsroom buyouts, eliminates public editor post|work=USA TODAY|access-date=2017-06-04|language=en}}</ref>\n* [[Daniel Okrent]] (2003\u20132005) \n* [[Byron Calame]] (2005\u20132007)\n* [[Clark Hoyt]] (2007\u20132010)\n* [[Arthur S. Brisbane]] (2010\u20132012)\n* [[Margaret Sullivan (journalist)|Margaret Sullivan]] (2012\u20132016)\n* [[Elizabeth Spayd]] (2016\u20132017)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{NY Times}}\n\n[[Category:The New York Times people|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of people by company|The New York Times]]\n[[Category:Employees by company]]\n", "name_user": "Kaltenmeyer", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up,typo(s) fixed: ,  \u2192 ,", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_The_New_York_Times_employees"}
